name: MEGA-IDEA iCharger - Battery Charging and Activation Tool
description:
Features
One-click activation
Non breaking cable
Support mainstream models
Automatic fast charging
Real time current and voltage
Multiple power supply modes
Automatic recognition
Instructions:
Power on: You can use type-c or alligator clip to power on (USB only works as output). After power on, the blue indicator light on the upper left will be on.
Connect the battery: Find the corresponding models position to connect.
One-click activation: Just click the activation button, and it will switch to automatic quick charge after activation.
Automatic power off: The battery will automatically cut off after being fully charged, and the indicator light will turn blue.
